    <item>
      <title>Test your layouts in Edge Rails</title>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://rubyonrails.org"&gt;Ruby on Rails&lt;/a&gt; sets what layout was rendered in the response object as of &lt;a href="http://dev.rubyonrails.org/changeset/4346"&gt;changeset 4346&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Now you can use this if you render different layouts based on conditions in your action:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class="typocode"&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class="typocode_default "&gt;def assert_layout_is(layout)
  assert_equal layout, File.basename(@response.layout, '.*')
end&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
